
<p>The <em>Turn A Gundam</em> movies were released on February of 2002 to much excitement. The Winter 2002 issue of <em>Gundam Ace</em> features a 4-page retrospective one-shot by Hajime Yamamura. They recall their thoughts about the TV show and look forward to the release of the movies. </p>


